This operation returns active team members by activity team segment identifiers.

## Service limit

A service limit constrains the number of identifiers and teams that can be processed in a single request.

* The __Number of Identifiers and Teams__ cannot exceed 10.

Refer to the [Limits](doc:limits-doc) topic for more information.

The associated Access Control Points are WFA_WORK_INTEGRATION_API and WFA_VIEW_TEAM_ACTIVITY_EVENT_MEMBERS.

## Example call

